title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E93 - Bats Out of Hell
description: Brian Wayne Foster is joined by Sam Riegel, Liam O'Brien, Travis Willingham, and Noelle Stevenson for Talks Machina! This week, they discuss Critical Role episode 93, give away GIF and fan art of the week prizes, and answer questions!
